#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Create a stunning <strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">website</font></strong> and start receiving orders directly in "
"Odoo. Go live with your <strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">E-shop</font></strong> in a few minutes."
msgstr ""
"Lav en flot <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">hjemmeside</font></"
"strong> og modtag ordrer direkte i Odoo. Gå live med din <strong><font class="
"\"text-o-color-1\">netbutik</font></strong> på få minutter."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "Discover more about Odoo by diving into our"
msgstr "Få mere at vide om Odoo i vores"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Discover the basics of this package and explore all the possibilities Odoo "
"offers to improve your experience."
msgstr ""
"Få indsigt i de grundlæggende funktioner i denne pakke, og udforsk de mange "
"muligheder, Odoo tilbyder, for at optimere din oplevelse."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "Do you want to go further?"
msgstr "Vil du tage det et skridt videre?"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Don't forget to hit the \"Order\" button each time you change an order. This"
" will forward the order to the Kitchen Display."
msgstr ""
"Husk at klikke på knappen \"Ordre\" hver gang, du ændrer en ordre. Det "
"videresender ordren til køkkenskærmen."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Each order will be sent to your preparation displays and if you don't "
"configure a payment terminal for each, they can pay directly online."
msgstr ""
"Hver ordre sendes til klargøringsdisplayet, og hvis du ikke konfigurerer en "
"betalingsterminal for hver, kan de betale direkte online."

#. module: fast_food
#: model:loyalty.program,name:fast_food.loyalty_program_2
msgid "Foodie Card"
msgstr "Foodie-kort"

#. module: fast_food
#: model:loyalty.reward,description:fast_food.loyalty_reward_1
msgid "Free Product - Cheese Burger"
msgstr "Gratis produkt – Cheeseburger"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "From the Point of Sale, open your register on the main dashboard."
msgstr "Åbn din kasse via hoveddashboardet i POS-appen."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "Hello there!"
msgstr "Hej!"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you navigate to your Purchase App, you can see a new Purchase Order that "
"is ready to be sent. You can choose a packaging if your product has an "
"existing one."
msgstr ""
"Når du åbner Indkøbsappen, vil du se en ny ordre klar til afsendelse. Du kan "
"vælge en emballage, hvis der allerede er en tilknyttet dit produkt."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you want to assign them an Odoo user account, you can select a related "
"user in the \"HR Settings\" tab."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du vil tildele dem en Odoo-brugerkonto, kan du vælge den ønskede bruger "
"under fanen \"HR-indstillinger\"."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you want to execute a practical guided tour of this module, you should "
"Import demo data and try the Demo - Use Case. (In the next Knowledge "
"Article)"
msgstr ""
"Hvis du vil gennemgå en praktisk rundvisning af dette modul, bør du "
"importere demodata og afprøve demoens brugsscenarie (som beskrevet i næste "
"artikel i Vidensdelingsappen)"

#. module: fast_food
#: model:product.template,name:fast_food.product_product_57_product_template
msgid "Ketchup 500ml"
msgstr "Ketchup 500 ml"

#. module: fast_food
#: model:planning.role,name:fast_food.planning_role_3
msgid "Kitchen"
msgstr "Køkken"

#. module: fast_food
#: model:loyalty.program,portal_point_name:fast_food.loyalty_program_2
msgid "Loyalty point(s)"
msgstr "Loyalitetspoint"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Make them pay the orders to release the table and continue your service."
msgstr ""
"Få kunderne til at betale for deres ordrer, så bordet frigives, og du kan "
"fortsætte din vagt."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage Loyalty Programs and many other kind of promotions, gifts and coupons"
" in the related page in your Point of Sales App &gt; Products."
msgstr ""
"Håndtér loyalitetsprogrammer samt forskellige typer tilbud, gaver og "
"rabatkuponer på den tilknyttede side i din POS-app under &gt; Produkter."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage all your communication channels in one place with Odoo <strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">Marketing Automation</font></strong>, <strong><font"
" class=\"text-o-color-1\">Email Marketing</font></strong>, <strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">Social Media Marketing</font></strong>, and "
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">SMS Marketing</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"Styr alle dine kommunikationskanaler på ét sted med Odoo <strong><font class="
"\"text-o-color-1\">Automatiseret marketing</font></strong>, <strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">E-mailmarketing</font></strong>, <strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">Markedsføring på sociale medier</font></strong> og "
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">SMS-marketing</font></strong>."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage recurring tasks and never forget any replenishment or cleaning with "
"the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Project App</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"Håndtér tilbagevendende opgaver, og glem aldrig en genopfyldning af din "
"lagerbeholdning eller rengøring med <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">"
"Projektappen</font></strong>."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage your accounting easier than ever with a completely integrated "
"environment. (<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Accounting "
"App</font></strong>)"
msgstr ""
"Din bogføring klares nemmere end nogensinde med et fuldt integreret miljø. "
"(<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Bogføringsapp</font></strong>)"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo also provides easy self ordering possibilities. Print a specific QR "
"code for each table on your Point of Sale settings and allow your customer "
"to order directly on their mobile phone."
msgstr ""
"Odoo giver dig også nemme selvbestillingsmuligheder. Udskriv en unik QR-kode "
"til hvert bord i dine POS-indstillinger, så kunderne kan bestille direkte "
"fra deres mobiltelefon."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo is entirely integrated into an App. Download it to turn your phone into"
" an additional cashier (and much more)."
msgstr ""
"Odoo er fuldt integreret i én app. Download den, og forvandl din telefon til "
"et værktøj, hvormed du kan bruge din telefon som et ekstra kasseapparat "
"(m.m.)."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "Odoo offers you infinite possibilities, such as :"
msgstr "Odoo giver dig ubegrænsede muligheder, såsom:"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Of course, this is just an overview of the features included in this "
"package. Feel free to add new apps, delete/modify demo data, and test "
"everything around!"
msgstr ""
"Oversigten viser naturligvis kun de funktioner, der følger med pakken. Du "
"kan tilføje nye apps, redigere eller slette demodata og prøve dig frem!"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once the products are there, you can click the \"Receipt\" smart button to "
"validate your receipt and add these new products to your stock."
msgstr ""
"Når produkterne er modtaget, kan du klikke på den intelligente knap "
"\"Kvittering\" for at godkende kvitteringen og tilføje produkterne til din "
"lagerbeholdning."

#. module: fast_food
#: model:pos.payment.method,name:fast_food.pos_payment_method_2
msgid "Online Payment"
msgstr "Onlinebetaling"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Organise your events and connect with your customers easily with the<strong>"
" <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Events App</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"Brug <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Arrangementerappen</font></"
"strong> til at arrangere dine begivenheder og nemt komme i kontakt med dine "
"kunder."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "Plan your services easily using the Planning App."
msgstr "Nem planlægning af vagter med Planlægningsappen."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "Reach us"
msgstr "Kontakt os"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Reordering rules are displayed in the smart buttons on top of your product. "
"You can see a minimum quantity, and a maximum. Each time the forecast stock "
"lowers beneath the minimum stock, it automatically creates a purchase order "
"to replenish to the maximum quantity."
msgstr ""
"Genbestillingsregler vises via de intelligente knapper øverst på produktet. "
"Her kan du se en minimums- og maksimumsmængde. Når lagerbeholdningen falder "
"under minimum, oprettes automatisk en indkøbsordre for at genopfylde til "
"maksimumsmængden."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Replenishment is essential but challenging for a bar owner to systematize."
msgstr ""
"Genopfyldning er vigtig, men kan være en udfordring at administrere for "
"barejere."

#. module: fast_food
#: model:product.template,name:fast_food.product_product_58_product_template
msgid "Sanitizer 250ml"
msgstr "Desinfektionsmiddel 250 ml"

#. module: fast_food
#: model:planning.role,name:fast_food.planning_role_1
msgid "Service"
msgstr "Tjenesteydelse"

#. module: fast_food
#: model:pos.payment.method,name:fast_food.pos_payment_method_1
msgid "Sodexo Card Payment"
msgstr "Sodexo-betalingskort"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Kitchen Displays</font></strong> "
"will ensure a great follow-up of every order in your bar and kitchen."
msgstr ""
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Køkkenskærmene</font></strong> sikrer "
"en enestående opfølgning af alle ordrer i din bar og i dit køkken."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The kiosk layout is optimized for vertical usage, as most booths use that "
"kind of display."
msgstr ""
"Kiosklayoutet er optimeret til vertikal brug, da de fleste diske anvender "
"denne type skærm."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The stock is only updated when you close your register. Let's do it before "
"continuing to the next step."
msgstr ""
"Lagerbeholdningen opdateres kun, når du lukker din kasse. Lad os gøre det, "
"inden vi går videre til næste trin."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"These all go free in your current subscription; feel free to explore! 🙃"
msgstr ""
"De er alle inkluderet i dit nuværende abonnement. Gå straks på opdagelse i "
"dem! 🙃"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "Use case:"
msgstr "Brugsscenarie:"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Inventory App</font></strong>"
" to manage your stock and receive products."
msgstr ""
"Brug <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Lagerappen</font></strong> til "
"at håndtere din lagerbeholdning og modtage produkter."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Planning App</font></strong> "
"to schedule and share your shifts with your employees."
msgstr ""
"Brug <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Planlægningsappen</font></"
"strong> til at planlægge og dele dine vagter med dine medarbejdere."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Point of Sale</font></strong>"
" at the desk for your sales. You can also download the Odoo Mobile App on "
"any phone to take orders. And create <strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">Kiosks </font><font class=\"text-o-color-5\"><span style=\"font-"
"weight: normal;\">or QR Codes</span></font></strong> to ensure self-"
"ordering."
msgstr ""
"Brug <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">POS</font></strong> på disken "
"til dine salg. Du kan også downloade Odoo Mobilapp på alle telefoner for at "
"modtage ordrer, og oprette <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">kiosker</"
"font> <font class=\"text-o-color-5\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">"
"eller QR-koder</span></font></strong> for at tilbyde selvbestilling."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Purchase App</font></strong> "
"to reorder your products."
msgstr ""
"Brug <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Indkøbsappen</font></strong> til "
"at genbestille dine produkter."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:web_tour.tour,rainbow_man_message:fast_food.knowledge_tour
msgid "Welcome! Happy exploring."
msgstr "Velkommen! God fornøjelse med at gå på opdagelse."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or go even further?"
msgstr ""
"Vil du gerne tale med os om dit Odoo-setup eller drøfte nogle spørgsmål mere "
"detaljeret?"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can access every installed App in your Odoo database on your main "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Du kan tilgå alle installerede apps i din Odoo-database direkte fra "
"hoveddashboardet."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can easily edit the floor map by clicking \"Edit plan\" in the top-right"
" menu when on the table selection step of your Point of Sale."
msgstr ""
"Du kan nemt redigere plantegningen ved at klikke på \"Redigér plantegning\" "
"øverst til højre i bordvalgsfasen i dit kassesystem."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can now email your Request for Proposal to your vendor or confirm it "
"manually."
msgstr ""
"Du kan nu e-maile din tilbudsanmodning til din leverandør og bekræfte den "
"manuelt."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can see that there is a reordering rule configured for this product if "
"you go to Inventory &gt; Products &gt; Blond Beer"
msgstr ""
"Du kan se, at en genbestillingsregel er konfigureret for dette produkt, når "
"du går til Lager &gt; Produkter &gt; Lys øl"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You completed that demo use case! There are millions of other ways to adapt "
"your Odoo setup to fit your business needs."
msgstr ""
"Du har nu gennemført demoens brugsscenarie. Odoo kan tilpasses på utallige "
"måder, så løsningen matcher netop din virksomheds behov."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You currently have two steps in your Kitchen Displays: one for the "
"kitchen/bar and one for the service. You can configure steps in the kitchen "
"display configuration menu."
msgstr ""
"På nuværende tidspunkt har du to trin på din køkkenskærm: ét til køkken/bar "
"og ét til din vagt. Du kan konfigurere trinnene i konfigurationsmenuen på "
"køkkenskærmen."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You didn't import demo data? You can still do it. Go to Apps &gt; Industries"
" &gt; Upgrade your Fast Food Restaurant package and check the related box."
msgstr ""
"Har du ikke importeret demodata endnu? Du kan stadig nå det. Gå til Apps &gt;"
" Brancher &gt; Opgradér din pakke til fastfoodrestauranter, og markér det "
"relevante felt."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You have two main possibilities in Odoo to ease your replenishment process."
msgstr ""
"Du har i Odoo to primære muligheder at forenkle din genopfyldningsproces på."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You just installed the Odoo for Fast Food Restaurant package. By doing so, "
"we have installed many necessary apps to run your restaurant efficiently."
msgstr ""
"Du har netop installeret Odoos pakke til fastfoodrestauranter. Når pakken "
"installeres, medfølger mange nødvendige apps, der sikrer en effektiv drift "
"af din restaurant."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You should be able to execute the following flows to have an overview of "
"various actions you can quickly execute with this package using Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Med denne pakke i Odoo kan du gennemføre følgende flows for hurtigt at få "
"overblik over de forskellige processer."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Your demo database comes with a kiosk to allow your customer to take orders "
"on your booths. Go to the Point of Sale App and select your kiosk to see how"
" it looks and try it!"
msgstr ""
"Din demodatabase inkluderer en kiosk, så kunderne kan afgive ordrer direkte "
"ved disken. Gå til POS-appen, vælg din kiosk for at se, hvordan den "
"fungerer, og prøv den!"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Your orders will automatically move from a step to another while you move it"
" on your preparation display."
msgstr ""
"Dine ordrer flyttes automatisk fra et trin til et andet, når du flytter dem "
"på dit klargøringsdisplay."

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "academy"
msgstr "akademi"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "and"
msgstr "og"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "documentation"
msgstr "dokumentation"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "if you need help! <br/>"
msgstr ", hvis du har brug for hjælp! <br/>"

#. module: fast_food
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fast_food.welcome_article_body
msgid "request a demo"
msgstr "anmode om en demo"
